{"about_the_game":"Inspired by the fascinating story of life on Earth, Creaturing - Sea Wonders allows you to create, control, test and share physic-based sea creatures and discover evolution through surprising challenges!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> CREATE</h2> <br>Use the flexible creature building system to create awesome physics based sea creatures of all shapes and sizes with all sorts of abilities! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/TrailerShark2.gif?t=1726759626\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DISCOVER EVOLUTION THROUGH SURPRISING CHALLENGES</h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> To survive as a crab, eat your own babies!<br></li><li> As a lobster, fight for a place to lay your eggs!<br> </li><li> As a pufferfish, create art to attract a mate! <br></li><li> And much more! </li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/TrailerTreeOfLife2.gif?t=1726759626\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> CONTROL</h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Move your creatures with the help of mechanical parts like joints and thrusters! <br></li><li> Control your creatures' behavior using sensors and neural circuits inspired by electronics!<br> </li><li> Test the capacities of your creatures in lush and beautiful underwater environments!  </li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/TrailerLobster2.gif?t=1726759626\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> SHARE</h2> <br>Share your realistic or whimsical creatures on the Steam Workshop!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/TrailerMeduse.gif?t=1726759626\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726759626","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a